data.description: Check out this Pueblo West 4 bedroom Bi-level home - one owner with pride of ownership from the moment you step inside. With a living room and family room it's a great place to entertaining or to make great family memories!  As you relax on the back deck you will capture the breath taking mountain views with a glimpse of Lake Pueblo.  Schedule a showing today!
